    "created_at": "2015-08-31T08:39:24Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-08-31T08:39:24Z",
    "body": "I found that executing the \"hide\" command from the menu produces the desired result, though of course it's super-hacky.\n\n```\nmenu = Menu.getApplicationMenu()\nappMenu = menu.items[0].submenu\nhideMenuItem = appMenu.items[4]\nappMenu.delegate.executeCommand hideMenuItem.commandId\n```\n\nSo I guess my question becomes - is there a way to do this directly via the `app` api?\n"
  },
