    "created_at": "2015-08-31T09:01:05Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-08-31T09:01:05Z",
    "body": "Sorry I thought `app.hide` was implemented, you can use `Menu.sendActionToFirstResponder` to implement that:\n\n``` js\nMenu.sendActionToFirstResponder('hide:');\n```\n"
